<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Asynchronous</li>
  <li>Very high performance</li>
  <li>Fully customizable annotations</li>
  <li>In-built plugins (File and Console)</li>
  <li>Auto archive</li>
  <li>De-Identification</li>
  <li>Minimum configurations</li>
  <li>Encrypted audit trails</li>
  <li>Supports for Java, Scala and Groovy</li>
  <li>Rich extendible API – Custom/third party plugins can be implemented by via the API</li>
</ul>
